<style>
  .pakora-benefits {
    background-color: #1B2A4A;
    padding: 60px 20px;
  }
  .pakora-benefits__inner {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .pakora-benefits__heading {
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    margin: 0 0 40px;
    line-height: 1.3;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .pakora-benefits__grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 28px;
  }
  .pakora-benefit-card {
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 24px 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .pakora-benefit-card__icon {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .pakora-benefit-card__content { flex: 1; }
  .pakora-benefit-card__title {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .pakora-benefit-card__desc {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  @media (min-width: 750px) {
    .pakora-benefits { padding: 80px 40px; }
    .pakora-benefits__heading { font-size: 3.2rem; }
    .pakora-benefits__grid {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: stretch;
    }
    .pakora-benefit-card {
      flex-direction: column;
      flex: 1;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .pakora-benefit-card__title { font-size: 1.9rem; }
    .pakora-benefit-card__desc { font-size: 1.6rem; }
  }
</style>

<section class="pakora-benefits">
  <div class="pakora-benefits__inner">
    <h2 class="pakora-benefits__heading">DryStep Pro resuelve todo eso.</h2>
    <div class="pakora-benefits__grid">

      <div class="pakora-benefit-card">
        <span class="pakora-benefit-card__icon">💨</span>
        <div class="pakora-benefit-card__content">
          <h3 class="pakora-benefit-card__title">Seca en horas, no en días</h3>
          <p class="pakora-benefit-card__desc">Circulación de aire caliente uniforme que llega hasta el interior del zapato. Sin deformar. Sin dañar.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pakora-benefit-card">
        <span class="pakora-benefit-card__icon">✨</span>
        <div class="pakora-benefit-card__content">
          <h3 class="pakora-benefit-card__title">Elimina el olor definitivamente</h3>
          <p class="pakora-benefit-card__desc">Tecnología de esterilización que destruye las bacterias causantes del mal olor. No lo enmascara — lo elimina.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pakora-benefit-card">
        <span class="pakora-benefit-card__icon">❄️</span>
        <div class="pakora-benefit-card__content">
          <h3 class="pakora-benefit-card__title">Protege tu inversión</h3>
          <p class="pakora-benefit-card__desc">La humedad destruye el cuero y las suelas. DryStep Pro prolonga la vida útil de tus zapatos.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Pakora — Beneficios",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [{ "name": "Pakora — Beneficios" }]
}
{% endschema %}
